      <description>&lt;p&gt;This page is inspired from &lt;a href=&#34;https://wesbos.com/&#34;&gt;@wesbos&amp;rsquo;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://uses.tech/&#34;&gt;uses.tech&lt;/a&gt; page.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;This section was planned from the beginning of this blog.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Now it&amp;rsquo;s finally happening.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;This post lists all the tools and equipment I use day in and day out.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Some tools/tech I am using may not be ideal for everyone,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;But they are somehow working for me.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; Please don&amp;rsquo;t take this as any sort of recommendation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;svg display=&#34;none&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;symbol id=&#34;arrow&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;polyline&#xA;      points=&#34;7 10,12 15,17 10&#34;&#xA;      fill=&#34;none&#34;&#xA;      stroke=&#34;currentcolor&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&#xA;      stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;    /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/symbol&gt;&#xA;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;div id=&#34;timeline&#34; class=&#34;timeline&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;timeline__item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;timeline__item-header&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;button&#xA;      class=&#34;timeline__arrow&#34;&#xA;      type=&#34;button&#34;&#xA;      id=&#34;item1&#34;&#xA;      aria-labelledby=&#34;item1-name&#34;&#xA;      aria-expanded=&#34;false&#34;&#xA;      aria-controls=&#34;item1-ctrld&#34;&#xA;      aria-haspopup=&#34;true&#34;&#xA;      data-item=&#34;1&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;      &lt;svg&#xA;        class=&#34;timeline__arrow-icon&#34;&#xA;        viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&#xA;        width=&#34;24px&#34;&#xA;        height=&#34;24px&#34;&#xA;      &gt;&#xA;        &lt;use href=&#34;#arrow&#34; /&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/button&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;timeline__dot&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span id=&#34;item1-name&#34; class=&#34;timeline__meta&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;